HOW TO INSTALL THIS DEMONSTRATION TO YOUR HD:
=============================================

A. SIMPLY COPY ALL FILES FROM THESE TWO ARCHIVES TO A DIRECTORY OF YOUR OWN
   CHOICE ON YOUR HARDDRIVE (TAKES UP ABOUT 2.2 MB OF HD CAPACITY).

B. CHANGE DIRECTORY TO WHERE YOU COPIED ALL THE FILES TO. NO ASSIGNS NEEDED!

C. START THE DEMO BY EXECUTING THE LOADERFILE: "MELCHIOR.EXE".


NOTE 1: SINCE THE DEMO REQUIRES QUITE A LOT OF CHIP-MEM, YOU'LL PROBABLY HAVE
        TO RUN IT WITHOUT STARTUP-SEQUENCE, IF YOU HAVEN'T GOT ANY ADDITIONAL
        MEMORY (FAST/CHIP).

NOTE 2: IF YOU HAVE ENOUGH MEMORY, YOU CAN JUST CRUNCH 'PART1.OBJ' AND
        'PART2.OBJ' WITH WHATEVER CRUNCHER YOU PREFER. WE DID DO SOME TESTING
        WITH DIFFERENT CRUNCHERS, BUT THERE WASN'T ENOUGH FREE MEMORY ON A
        PLAIN A1200 TO DECRUNCH THEM, AND WE WOULDN'T RISK THAT IT DID NOT
        WORK ON ALL AMIGAS IF CRUNCHED WITH TITANICS (CRAP CRUNCHER!).
        ANYWAY, IF YOU HAVEN'T GOT ANY EXTRA MEMORY - ENJOY FAST LOADING!


ENJOY THIS PIECE AND.... SEE YOU AT `SOUTH SEALAND 95'!

ASCII BY MORPH (THANKS MAN!)


